nodes.text: A clone trooper served alongside High Jedi General Obi-Wan Kenobi during the Clone Wars.

During the Clone Wars, a clone trooper was stationed on the Venator-class Star Destroyer known as the Negotiator with Jedi General Obi-Wan Kenobi when General Grievous's fleet slipped out of hyperspace and launched an all-out attack on Kenobi's ships. This trooper helped fend off the droid boarding parties onboard the Negotiator and attempted to jump on Grievous. However, he was caught and thrown to the ground before being strangled by the cyborg general. When the fighting came to a pause, Kenobi witnessed the trooper being strangled to death and swore that Grievous would pay for murdering the trooper.
